<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>The <link linkend="_class_standard_menu">StandardMenu</link> class represents a standard menu implementation. </para>



<para>This class inherits from the <link linkend="_class_i_menu">IMenu</link> interface and the <link linkend="_class_named_thread">NamedThread</link> class. It provides functionality to display and interact with a menu. </para>
</section>
